          </span>
        </div>
        
        <div class="border-t-2 border-b-2 pt-1 border-black items-center flex" >
          <span
            class="text-4xl max-lg:text-3xl max-md:text-2xl max-sm:text-sm font-bold mr-1 primary-color symphony"
